# Define the Transcript Redaction Boundary

## Question

Transcripts contain secrets, tokens, customer content, and third-party
text. Observation pages are publications (rendered on the paper). Define the
redaction pass the distiller MUST apply — reuse the wiki's redact.ts
patterns or a shared library? — plus enforcement point (before persistence,
per the privacy resolution: never store what can't be shown) and what the
secure-mode masking marks in observation pages. Inherits, does not reopen,
the closed privacy boundaries ticket.
